s_title: Golf Magazine - 36 Great Holes Starring Fred Couples
s_synopsis:
Take control of 24 different digitized golfers playing in 27 historic courses in the U.S. including Disney's Eagle Pines and Tidewater Golf Club, playing 36 authentic holes.
There are seven different modes (Stroke Play, Tournament, Skins, Shoot-out, Scramble, Practice and Match Play) and three different types of golf club heads including wood, metal and graphite.
